18#include "ODEAN8Reader.h"
19#include "ODUPCEANCommon.h"
20#include "BitArray.h"
21#include "BarcodeFormat.h"
22#include "DecodeStatus.h"
23#include "ZXContainerAlgorithms.h"
24
25namespace ZXing {
26namespace OneD {
27
28BarcodeFormat
29EAN8Reader::expectedFormat() const
30{
31 return BarcodeFormat::EAN_8;
32}
33
34BitArray::Range
35EAN8Reader::decodeMiddle(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin, std::string& resultString) const
36{
37 BitArray::Range next = {begin, row.end()};
38 const BitArray::Range notFound = {begin, begin};
39
40 for (int x = 0; x < 4; x++) {
41 if (DecodeDigit(&next, UPCEANCommon::L_PATTERNS, &resultString) == -1)
42 return notFound;
43 }
44
45 if (!ReadGuardPattern(&next, UPCEANCommon::MIDDLE_PATTERN))
46 return notFound;
47
48 for (int x = 0; x < 4; x++) {
49 if (DecodeDigit(&next, UPCEANCommon::L_PATTERNS, &resultString) == -1)
50 return notFound;
51 }
52 return {begin, next.begin};
53}
